<h1>Deployment & Security</h1>
<p>Stateless core: scale horizontally. Use environment isolation for provider keys.</p>
<h2>Security Practices</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Keys loaded at process start; never logged.</li>
  <li>Planned: secret rotation hooks.</li>
  <li>Planned: per-request audit metadata.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Self-Hosting</h2>
<p>Runtime embed or service wrapper. Minimal dependencies keep footprint small.</p>
